{"tid":1920670,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"我地再無咩能力犧牲任何人 ，黎換取我地保持熱度","createTime":"2020-03-11T15:11:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-11T15:25:05.000Z","uid":54200,"like":25,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"bae0cd0b20a4248b28254075925fea34e34a3b47","tid":1920670,"uid":54200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T15:11:16.000Z","msg":"面對法律嘅崩壞<br />\n手足過程係點比人屈打成招<br />\n係庭上已經唔係考慮因素 <br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n知唔知爆炸品手足會點？</span><br />\n最高終身 其他20年起跳<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/32n6dT6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F32n6dT6.png&h=2d1d550e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">知唔知屠龍小隊會點？</span><br />\n無牌管有槍械 <br />\n14年起跳<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">知唔知鎅頸手足</span><br />\n謀殺都係終身<br />\n<br />\nhey 香港人，唔好指責同分化同路人，<br />\n對敵人寬容，對同路人苛刻<br />\n<br />\n2020全民公投<br />\n搶攻立法會議席<br />\n從下而上改變制度<br />\n一票不投建制派"},{"pid":"ebccd1f9c50150c72d11e9fd196a400d33126c38","tid":1920670,"uid":54200,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T15:11:26.000Z","msg":"第一次我地6月15犧牲左梁凌杰<br />\n換取左我哋2百萬人嘅遊行<br />\n<br />\n第二次我地犧牲左一位少女<br />\n換取左香港有事最多人嘅7月1日大遊行<br />\n<br />\n第三次我地犧牲左隻眼<br />\n黎換取我哋保持一息間熱度"},{"pid":"20551d57b13bcf10735f4d98d196c2f6df48275b","tid":1920670,"uid":54200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T15:12:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f552852236df8f40c3914ca149b5f5889546138","tid":1920670,"uid":54200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T15:12:18.000Z","msg":"自推1"},{"pid":"429dccce21e76264ea9b23a3f521cf049e7027ef","tid":1920670,"uid":54200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T15:12:38.000Z","msg":"自推2"},{"pid":"ac0576c84a0fd3d4ba0fc00f1c41dea7ae